elements.caption: The Solar Panel Overview tile provides a quick overview of the usage of produced PV energy, consumption, import, and export. All source variables require active logging. Expected values: kWh. Daily consumption can optionally be calculated by the module. A battery storage is optionally supported.
Example of a fully configured tile

items.caption: All variables must have active logging. The tile reads the values of the current day from the archive. Unit = kWh.
